  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-provider LLM support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, Mistral, OpenRouter)",
    "Fluent chat API with tool calling and streaming",
    "Document extraction from PDFs, Word docs, images, and spreadsheets",
    "Multiple extraction strategies (simple, sequential, parallel, double-pass)",
    "Native Laravel integration with Livewire support",
    "Type-safe structured data extraction with JSON Schema validation",
    "Embeddings generation for RAG applications",
    "Pre-built tools including Eloquent CRUD operations"
